Second, separately, define what a Multi-Agent System (MAS) is, explaining the concepts of agents, environment, and interaction protocols. Third, after *both* definitions are complete, analyze and explain three distinct ways LLMs can be utilized *within* a Multi-Agent System to enhance its capabilities. Finally, synthesize these findings into a concise report summarizing the definitions and the integration points.

Second, separately, define what a Multi-Agent System (MAS) is, explaining the concepts of agents, environment, and interaction protocols. Third, after *both* definitions are complete, analyze and explain three distinct ways LLMs can be utilized *within* a Multi-Agent System to enhance its capabilities.
